<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 00:50:34 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美韩防务谈判进展顺利，但 11 月并非硬性最后期限——美国官员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-south-korea-defense-talks-track-november-not-hard-deadline-us-official-2024-03-13/</link><description>拜登政府一名高级官员告诉路透社，美韩关于分担驻韩美军费用的谈判正在按计划进行，并且提前完成，但美方不一定会在 11 月美国大选之前看到一个严格的最后期限。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 23:51:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-south-korea-defense-talks-track-november-not-hard-deadline-us-official-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>据《卫报》报道，中国外长下周将访问澳大利亚</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-foreign-minister-visit-australia-next-week-guardian-reports-2024-03-13/</link><description>据《卫报》周四报道，中国外交部长王毅将于下周访问澳大利亚，北京和堪培拉之间的关系在经历多年的紧张关系后出现解冻。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 23:18:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-foreign-minister-visit-australia-next-week-guardian-reports-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>由于价格下跌打击高成本矿商，中国锂热潮放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-lithium-boom-slows-sagging-prices-batter-high-cost-miners-2024-03-13/</link><description>锂是电动汽车电池的关键原材料，其价格暴跌正在拖累中国的超轻金属开采，加上成本高昂的提取工艺，促使人们重新评估产量增长和新项目计划。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 23:07:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-lithium-boom-slows-sagging-prices-batter-high-cost-miners-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>保险公司友邦保险 (AIA) 2023 年新业务价值因香港销售强劲而飙升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/insurer-aias-2023-new-business-value-soars-strong-hong-kong-sales-2024-03-13/</link><description>周四，友邦保险集团报告称，由于受益于香港对其保险产品的强劲需求，该公司的年度新业务价值 (VONB) 增长了 33%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 22:57:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/insurer-aias-2023-new-business-value-soars-strong-hong-kong-sales-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>随着南海紧张局势升级，菲律宾马科斯将于下周会见布林肯</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-marcos-meet-blinken-next-week-presidential-office-says-2024-03-13/</link><description>马尼拉领导人办公室周三晚间在一份声明中表示，菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯将于 3 月 19 日会见美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯，讨论合作和安全问题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 22:50:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-marcos-meet-blinken-next-week-presidential-office-says-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>生物技术行业协会将与中国药明康德分家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/biotech-trade-association-split-with-chinas-wuxi-apptec-2024-03-13/</link><description>总部位于华盛顿的一家代表生物技术公司的全球贸易协会正在采取措施，与中国会员药明康德“分离”，根据该协会新任首席执行官周三的一封信。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 22:28:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/biotech-trade-association-split-with-chinas-wuxi-apptec-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>耶伦表示，随着中国增加出口，美国的目标是确保国内电动汽车制造商取得成功</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/yellen-says-us-moving-ensure-domestic-ev-maker-success-despite-chinas-exports-2024-03-13/</link><description>美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦周三表示，面对中国不断增长的电动汽车出口和巨额政府补贴，总统乔·拜登的政府正在采取措施确保国内电动汽车（EV）行业的成功。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 20:28:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/yellen-says-us-moving-ensure-domestic-ev-maker-success-despite-chinas-exports-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>泽连斯基幕僚长与中国大使讨论和平前景及峰会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/zelenskiys-chief-staff-discusses-peace-prospects-summit-with-chinese-ambassador-2024-03-13/</link><description>乌克兰总统泽伦斯基的幕僚长周三会见了中国驻基辅大使，讨论了中国特使上周访问基辅的事宜，以及专门讨论与俄罗斯长达两年的冲突的世界峰会的筹备工作。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 18:59:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/zelenskiys-chief-staff-discusses-peace-prospects-summit-with-chinese-ambassador-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>麦当劳首席财务官表示海外销售将进一步疲软，中东和中国受到打击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/mcdonalds-cfo-says-overseas-sales-weaken-more-middle-east-china-hit-2024-03-13/</link><description>麦当劳首席财务官伊恩·博登(Ian Borden)周三表示，受中东冲突和中国需求疲软的压力，麦当劳本季度的国际销售额将连续下降，导致其股价早盘下跌2%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 14:22:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/mcdonalds-cfo-says-overseas-sales-weaken-more-middle-east-china-hit-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国委员会敦促对涉嫌在中国捕鱼的朝鲜劳工采取行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-commission-urges-action-alleged-north-korean-labor-china-fishing-2024-03-13/</link><description>美国国会一个委员会呼吁拜登政府对中国渔业中涉及朝鲜工人的强迫劳动行为采取行动，称向美国消费者销售海鲜可能有助于为朝鲜的武器计划提供资金。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 14:03:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-commission-urges-action-alleged-north-korean-labor-china-fishing-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国国防部称与北约举行军事人员对话</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-defence-ministry-says-it-held-military-staff-dialogue-with-nato-2024-03-13/</link><description>中国国防部的一份声明称，中国和北约周三在北京举行第八次军事安全政策对话。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 12:06:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-defence-ministry-says-it-held-military-staff-dialogue-with-nato-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国立法者提出立法，寻求对中国房地产购买进行更多审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-lawmakers-propose-legislation-seeking-more-scrutiny-chinese-real-estate-2024-03-13/</link><description>两名美国议员将于周四提出立法，大幅扩大政府对来自中国和其他构成国家安全担忧的外国买家购买房地产的外国投资审查。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 11:37:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-lawmakers-propose-legislation-seeking-more-scrutiny-chinese-real-estate-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>独家：意大利与中国奇瑞就汽车工厂进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-talks-with-chinas-chery-car-plant-2024-03-13/</link><description>两位消息人士告诉路透社，意大利政府正在与中国奇瑞汽车进行谈判，以吸引除 Stellantis 之外的另一家主要汽车制造商进入该国并增加国内汽车产量。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 11:34:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-talks-with-chinas-chery-car-plant-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车表示其ID.UNYX车型已获得中国政府批准</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-says-it-has-received-chinese-government-approval-idunyx-model-2024-03-13/</link><description>大众汽车集团（中国）周三表示，其唯一控股的合资企业安徽大众汽车的首款车型已获得中国政府批准。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 10:11:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-says-it-has-received-chinese-government-approval-idunyx-model-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国众议院通过法案迫使字节跳动剥离 TikTok 或面临禁令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-house-vote-force-bytedance-divest-tiktok-or-face-ban-2024-03-13/</link><description>美国众议院周三以压倒性多数通过了一项法案，该法案将给予 TikTok 的中国所有者字节跳动大约六个月的时间剥离这款短视频应用程序的美国资产，否则将面临禁令，这是自特朗普政府以来该应用程序面临的最大威胁。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 10:01:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-house-vote-force-bytedance-divest-tiktok-or-face-ban-2024-03-13/</guid></item></channel></rss>